1
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:16,800
After Zhao died,

2
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,520
I was devastated.

3
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,120
To protect myself,

4
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,280
and to one day

5
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:30,320
avenge him,

6
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,680
I have been waiting for an opportunity.

7
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,560
Not until Wang

8
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,800
and Miss Su appeared,

9
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:47,280
did I have hope.

10
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,080
Everything before

11
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:55,840
was to test your character.

12
00:00:58,320 --> 00:00:59,320
I'm sorry.

13
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,400
Song Wencai.

14
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,000
How many lives has your Song family ruined

15
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,120
because of

16
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,320
an antique?

17
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,890
What is the secret behind all this?

18
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:15,560
I...

19
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,410
How dare you!

20
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,600
Good job.

21
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,200
You have a promising future.

22
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,850
If there's a chance,

23
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,740
I'll let you be my apprentice.

24
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:35,720
Come here.

25
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,160
It really was you

26
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,720
setting me up.

27
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,320
Director Song,

28
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,600
isn't it a bit late

29
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,600
to realize that now?

30
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:57,759
Song Ping,

31
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,380
since you're here,

32
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,640
tell us the truth.

33
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,840
Why did you kill so many women?

34
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,160
I don't know what you're talking about.

35
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,090
I'm telling you,

36
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,660
let my son go right now,

37
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,120
or I won't let you off.

38
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,900
Let's talk nicely.

39
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,440
Don't be so angry.

40
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,000
Mayor Su,

41
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:20,240
we're old friends.

42
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,380
For the position of mayor,

43
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,920
come at me if you have a problem.

44
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,360
Why drag my son into this?

45
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,800
Look at what you're saying.

46
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,800
I wouldn't dare.

47
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,600
You wouldn't?

48
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,700
Then let him go now.

49
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,720
You can't let him go.

50
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:35,050
You don't need to be afraid of him anymore.

51
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:37,840
This is official business between Director Song and me.

52
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,440
It's not your place to speak.

53
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,440
However,

54
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,320
since it's official business,

55
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,720
we have to go by the book.

56
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:53,180
I believe in Director Song's character.

57
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,920
If he says he doesn't know,

58
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,120
then he doesn't know.

59
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:57,920
But,

60
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:01,040
regarding the crimes committed by Song Wencai,

61
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,900
he has already confessed to them.

62
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,960
And we have witnesses,

63
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,800
so there's no denying it.

64
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,480
According to the laws of the Republic of China,

65
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:13,010
if there are no new developments in this case,

66
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,600
Song Wencai will be

67
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,280
executed on the spot.

68
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,520
Su.

69
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,000
I didn't expect

70
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,200
you to be so ruthless.

71
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,500
I'm just acting according to the law.

72
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,500
Director Song,

73
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,640
regarding this case,

74
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,920
do you have anything else to say?

75
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,600
Save me!

76
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:34,760
Save me!

77
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,360
Song Ping,

78
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:38,050
are you really going to watch your son die?

79
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,320
I, Song Ping, swear here

80
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,680
that whoever dares to touch my son today,

81
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,940
I will make sure you die a horrible death.

82
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,400
Director Song,

83
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,460
what are you doing?

84
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:49,820
Don't move.

85
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,960
I'm very curious.

86
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,920
How exactly are you going to kill me?

87
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,960
Mr. Song,

88
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,800
when your head gets chopped off,

89
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,560
it will hurt a little.

90
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,610
Bear with it.

91
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,660
Don't you dare.

92
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,680
Don't believe me?

93
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,279
Try me.

94
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,260
Save me.

95
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,410
I don't want to die, Father.

96
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,540
I'll give you one last chance.

97
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,610
Will you talk or not?

98
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,240
Save me.

99
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,280
I'm your son. You can't abandon me.

100
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,480
You still won't talk?

101
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,760
I...

102
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,560
In that case,

103
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,400
carry out the execution.

104
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:43,400
No.

105
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,440
The mayor usually looks like a pushover.

106
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,680
But when he gets serious,

107
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,880
he's quite ruthless.

108
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,200
Damn it.

109
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,800
Who has the nerve

110
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,480
to mess with my uncle?

111
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,600
Uncle.

112
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,640
General.

113
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,000
Please forgive me

114
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,860
for not coming out to welcome you.

115
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,210
General.

116
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,800
Did you think you left no trace,

117
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,130
and I would be helpless?

118
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,860
When I realized I was tricked,

119
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,900
I already prepared a backup plan.

120
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,520
Now that the General is here,

121
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,000
hurry up and release him.

122
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,600
Warlord.

123
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,770
These people are absolutely lawless.

124
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,760
They actually framed my son,

125
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,320
used his life to threaten me,

126
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,840
and forced me to confess!

127
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,640
Damn it.

128
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,240
It seems to me that you all

129
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,200
have no respect for me at all.

130
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,840
The Warlord has spoken.

131
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:01,770
Release him now.

132
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,200
Song Ping.

133
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,520
I just gave you a chance.

134
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,200
You didn't cherish it.

135
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,760
So what?

136
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,720
The Warlord is here.

137
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,040
What else do you think you can do?

138
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,800
Release him!

139
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,040
My precious sword

140
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,960
only drinks the blood of the wicked,

141
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,660
and cares about nothing else.

142
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,000
Fine.

143
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,000
Wang Shiqi.

144
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,160
If you dare to do it in front of the Warlord,

145
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,520
and cut off my son's head,

146
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,780
I'll be your grandson!

147
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,080
You said it.

148
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,360
Grandson.

149
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,530
Three souls return.

150
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,460
Seven spirits suffer.

151
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,250
The golden sword executes.

152
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,640
No blood on the blade,

153
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,200
no head on the ground.

154
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,080
My son!

155
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,240
Song Ping.

156
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,560
It seems your son's crimes

157
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,610
are far less than yours.

158
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,280
My son!

159
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,400
Warlord.

160
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,800
Right in front of you,

161
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,240
he dared to cut off my son's head.

162
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,000
You must seek justice for me!

163
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,320
Damn it.

164
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,640
I see you really dare to

165
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:38,000
look down on me.

166
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,800
Take him down!

167
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,920
Warlord.

168
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,000
The country has its laws.

169
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,460
Song Wencai broke the law.

170
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,320
Wang Shiqi carried out the mayor's order.

171
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,320
What's his crime?

172
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,000
Warlord.

173
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,080
My daughter might be reckless,

174
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,800
but what she said is true.

175
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:57,000
Everyone here can testify.

176
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,159
Song Wencai

177
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,760
was indeed guilty of terrible crimes.

178
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:02,560
Killing him was the only way to appease the public.

179
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,400
Song Wencai murdered people.

180
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,460
He deserved to die.

181
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,460
Commander,

182
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,920
even if you are related to Song Ping,

183
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,800
you should know

184
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,440
the law is above everything.

185
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,000
Enough!

186
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,200
Damn it!

187
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,400
What do you mean the law is above everything?

188
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,460
I am the Commander.

189
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,940
I am above everything.

190
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,440
Whoever says another word

191
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,170
will be shot.

192
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,040
It's quite lively here.
